Text:
Isn't this missing the last page? 'cause after Eve says "I'll call Cecil." it feels like there's at least one page left at the end of this issue. 'cause, you know, in this comic, there's always a cliffhanger for us, and it feels like that it's missing here.
Well, anyone?

Sorry, i just caught up to this issue -that WAS the cliffhanger.

Btw i started Issue #1 on friday and just caught up to 93 and its WED - this is THE best comic ever! I could not put it down. WOW
